data.description: OPEN HOUSE 1/20-1/21 1-3PM! Custom built home far from the ordinary ranch. This residence offers almost 1,600 sq ft on the main floor with vaulted ceilings, hardwoods, & ceramic tile. Kitchen features custom cabinetry, granite countertops, & high-end appliances, complemented by a large walk-in pantry. Main floor hosts a master suite with a walk-in closet & bath. Additional conveniences include entry level laundry, 2 bedrooms, & full bath. Lower level features bamboo flooring, offers 2 large bedrooms, 3rd bath, family room, & ample storage - a potential mother-in-law suite. Recent upgrades include a 2018 HVAC replacement. Outdoor living is elevated with two decks perfect for entertaining. Minutes from 81, this home is situated in the Summer Dean neighborhood in North Roanoke County
